App-ZofCMS-Plugin-BoolSettingsManager

The module is a plugin for L<App::ZofCMS> that provides means to present
a user a form with a number of checkboxes that control boolean settings,
which are stored in a SQL database.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc App::ZofCMS::Plugin::BoolSettingsManager

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=App-ZofCMS-Plugin-BoolSettingsManager

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/App-ZofCMS-Plugin-BoolSettingsManager

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/App-ZofCMS-Plugin-BoolSettingsManager

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/App-ZofCMS-Plugin-BoolSettingsManager/


